    avatar: {fileID: 0}
    content: "Sau khi nh\u1EADn \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c th\u1EBB t\u1EEB ng\u01B0\u1EDDi
      ra v\xE0o, em h\xE3y c\u1EA7m sang b\xE0n b\xEAn ph\u1EA3i \u0111\u1EC3 check
